The http://peaceandfreedom.org/ Peace and Freedom Party, also known as Californias Feminist Socialist Political Party, is a California political party. According to a May 2008 report from the Yolo County elections office, the city of Davis has 72 registered Peace and Freedom members, or 0.21% of registered voters.Footnote(Yolo County Elections Office. http://www.yoloelections.org/voting/stats/sfiles/052208%20report%20of%20registration.pdf Report of Registration  State Reporting Districts. 20080522.)

Currently, no local representatives are members of the Peace and Freedom Party.
